text: Bonny Bonello (née Chesson, born 17 December 1950) is a Canadian equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Newark-on-Trent
